Version 2.0.0 - May 26 2014, by I. Volobouev

* Initial repackaging of the version 1.1 code from
  http://www.iro.umontreal.ca/~simardr/ksdir/

* Switched from C to C++ and changed all occurrences of malloc/free to
  automatic memory management by std::vector.

* Introduced "const" qualifiers in various places.

* Changed "int n" to "unsigned n" for the sample size.
